posts.name: Brad
posts.cooked: Is the 2023-chargedup.json April Tag location map that we would load into AprilTagFieldLayout bundled into wpilib 2023.1.1 as a resource, and if so what is the path to it?

posts.name: Weaver Goldman
posts.cooked: It isn’t in the initial release, but it will be included in the next release of wpilib.

posts.name: Peter Johnson
posts.cooked: I’ll add it would be impossible for us to include it in the kickoff release as we release several days before kickoff.

posts.name: DrewTheRat
posts.cooked:
I see a version of this file in the main branch here: allwpilib/2023-chargedup.json at main · wpilibsuite/allwpilib · GitHub

Is this a good version to use (until the next release is out)?

posts.name: Jp
posts.cooked: Is it already on the latest version? If yes, how can I use it?

It’s been added as of release 2023.2.1

Relevant API docs can be found here ; the json path is provided as AprilTagFields.k2023ChargedUp.m_resourceFile
